 * Warm, plain, honest. Render it on any page or article that carries affiliate
 * links; skip it on pages that don't.
 */
---

<aside class="affiliate-disclosure" role="note">
  <span class="affiliate-disclosure__label">A note on links</span>
  <p>
    Some links on this page are affiliate links — if you buy something through
    them, we may earn a small commission, at no extra cost to you. It never
    changes what we recommend. We only point to things we genuinely think are
